title: Goong S
resume: Goong S is a 2007 South Korean romantic comedy television series, starring Se7en, Huh E-jae, Park Shin-hye and Kang Doo. It is a spin-off of 2006 series Goong, and both were directed by Hwang In-roi of the production company Group Eight. Goong S aired on MBC from January 10 to March 15, 2007 on Wednesdays and Thursdays at 21:55 for 20 episodes.
